Drama starring Destiny Etiko, Stephen Odimgbe, Ebele Okaro

Will destiny succeed in bringing back the two lovers together once again?

programme.title: Apocalipse: A Guerra dos Mundos S1 E1
programme.desc: Deixando a Segunda Guerra Mundial para trs, as naes aliadas celebram vitria enquanto voltam paz mundial. No entanto, nos bastidores do ps-guerra, um confronto mais srio est prestes a surgir: a Guerra Fria.

programme.title: Apocalipse: A Guerra dos Mundos S1 E2
programme.desc: 1947. Temendo que uma Europa fragilizada possa ceder ao Comunismo, a Amrica lana o Plano Marshall, um apoio reconstruo para as naes europeias. Os franceses tambm precisam de ajuda na Indochina, onde Ho Chi Minh, escondido na selva, v o seu exrcito e poder crescer

programme.title: Apocalipse: A Guerra dos Mundos S1 E3
programme.desc: Setembro de 1950. Na Coreia, o conflito arrasta-se. Aps uma aterragem bem sucedida em Incheon, o General MacArthur e as suas tropas saem mais uma vez derrotadas perto do rio Yalu, onde enfrentam um novo inimigo: a China. Truman pondera a bomba atmica? Na Indochina, os franceses esto a ser derrotados.

programme.title: Apocalipse: A Guerra dos Mundos S1 E4
programme.desc: Maro de 1953. Estaline est morto. Depois de muitas e longas horas de agonia na sua propriedade, o "Pai dos Povos" agora nada mais do que um corpo embalsamado. Os seus potenciais sucessores rapidamente chegam para prestar a sua homenagem. Na Berlim de leste, uma onda de esperana envolve os trabalhadores alemes que esto contra o partido. Ser esta esperana aniquilada pelos tanques soviticos? Na sia, os conflitos graves esto a chegar ao fim. Depois das trguas de Panmunjom, os EUA abandonam a Coreia sem glria. As poucas tropas que permanecem no local aguardam, impacientes, uma visita de Marilyn Monroe. Entretanto, na Indochina, outro exrcito prepara um acontecimento muito menos emocionante. Os franceses esperam parar os Vietminh em Dien Bien Phu, uma aldeia rodeada de montanhas a quase 300 quilmetros de Hanoi. Contudo, os generais franceses mal suspeitavam que nesse preciso momento, o General Giap dos Vietminh e os seus conselheiros chineses estavam a engendrar um plano de batalha baseado numa armadilha: deixar as foras francesas instalar-se no vale Dien Bien Phu, rode-las e destru-las. O exrcito francs rapidamente deixa o pas, gravemente ferido e humilhado. Ho Chi Minh sai apenas parcialmente vitorioso. Durante as negociaes em Genebra, os seus camaradas chineses e soviticos no correspondem s expectativas, por receio de fazer escalar o conflito. Ho Chi Minh fica com o Vietname do norte, mas o sul continua nas mos do ocidente. O que ir Ho Chi Minh fazer?

programme.title: Apocalipse: A Guerra dos Mundos S1 E5
programme.desc: 24 de fevereiro de 1956. Durante o 20 congresso do Partido Comunista Sovitico, Khrushchev deixa toda a gente de boca aberta ao denunciar os crimes de Estaline. Sem negar a ideologia, o novo lder da URSS procura distanciar-se do seu antecessor e abrir-se ao mundo. O "Senhor K" est cheio de surpresas. Com que ento bebe Pepsi com Nixon e insiste em passar um dia na Disneyland quando visita a Amrica? Porm, por detrs desta mscara, o "carrasco da Ucrnia" no ser brando. Em 1956, no hesitou em esmagar a revolta em Budapeste com um banho de sangue. Agora, prepara-se para uma coexistncia com o recentemente eleito Presidente Kennedy que viria a ser tudo menos pacfica. O Muro de Berlim, a crise dos msseis de Cuba, para no falar na assistncia que presta a Ho Chi Minh na sua preparao para a reunificao. A Guerra do Vietname est prestes a comear. Kennedy tenta retaliar e envia conselheiros militares para treinar o exrcito do sul do Vietname. E, em Berlim, no dia 26 de junho de 1963, faz o seu famoso discurso carregado de esperana perante uma multido emocionada: "Ich bin ein Berliner!".

programme.title: Apocalipse: A Guerra dos Mundos S1 E6
programme.desc: 22 de novembro de 1963. O mundo inteiro est em choque. O Presidente Kennedy acabou de ser assassinado durante uma viagem a Dallas. At Khrushchev parece tocado pelas notcias trgicas. Numa coincidncia surpreendente, Diem, o presidente sul-vietnamita, havia sido assassinado vinte dias antes, num golpe organizado pelos seus generais. Os protagonistas mudam, mas a guerra do Vietname arrasta-se. O novo presidente dos EUA, Johnson, afunda ainda mais o seu pas no caos da guerra. Quase trs milhes de jovens conheceram o Inferno: a selva, o calor insuportvel e os Viet Cong, com os seus tneis e armadilhas. Pela primeira vez, a televiso desempenha um papel especial na guerra. Em 1968, os americanos descobrem o fiasco a acontecer no Vietname atravs de imagens da desastrosa ofensiva Tet transmitidas na TV. Massacres, abuso e tortura de soldados americanos e a derrota bvia do seu exrcito. Em breve, os EUA no tero alternativa a no ser retirar as tropas. Ser esta uma vitria do mundo comunista? Contudo, a URSS est na bancarrota. Enfraquecida pelas diversas campanhas pelo mundo, a Unio Sovitica perde no Afeganisto. Em breve, as repblicas "satlite" reclamam os seus direitos. Cada uma delas derruba o governo imposto por Moscovo. Em 1989, cai o Muro de Berlim, seguindo-se a exploso do imprio sovitico. A bandeira vermelha com estrela dourada desce das torres do Kremlin. o final da Guerra Fria. A guerra entre dois mundos chegou ao fim.

programme.title: Supercarros S1 E1
programme.desc: Neste episdio de Supercar Megabuild, Afzal Kahn e o seu departamento de pesquisa e desenvolvimento aceitam o desafio de transformar um Aston Martin Vantage V8 num supercarregado carro de corrida inspirado em GT. Ralph e Ranen, os crebros de engenharia por detrs do projecto embarcam numa misso para tornar este supercarro elegante num veculo de competio agressivo e super rpido e que ser legal para os clientes do Sr. Kahn. Para melhor compreenderem e se inspiraram nesta arte, iro at ao bero do "drifting" - Japo.

programme.title: Supercarros S1 E2
programme.desc: O guru da indstria automvel e designer Afzal Kahn tem uma ideia de um prottipo baseado num veculo muito familiar para ele - o Range Rover Evoque. Ele planeia transformar o crossover urbano no derradeiro todo-o-terreno, um veculo inspirado no Rally Paris-Dakar. uma viagem que far os engenheiros especialistas testar o veculo num dos ambientes mais extremos imaginveis, fabricar e instalar um kit de suspenso nico para o afastar ainda mais do cho, instalar luzes poderosas no tejadilho e coloc-lo num programa agressivo e inspirado no Dakar. programme.title: O Incrvel Dr. Pol S1 E1
programme.desc: Neste episdio de estreia, conhecemos Dr. Jan Pol, que, juntamente com a sua esposa Diane, gere uma clnica veterinria no meio da zona rural do Michigan. To trabalhador como excntrico, o Dr. Pol no menos do que uma lenda local dentro da comunidade graas sua abordagem da velha guarda e directa ao cuidado animal. Com a ajuda da sua colega Dr. Brenda, o Dr. Pol mantm um ritmo agitado enquanto cuida de animais de estimao e trata um grande leque de gado das quintas que o rodeiam. medida que o 30 aniversrio da clnica se aproxima, os Pols planeiam um churrasco de porco moda antiga para os seus empregados, clientes de longa data e antigos colegas. No meio dos convidados especiais encontramos o seu filho Charles, que vive em Los Angeles e decide prolongar a sua estadia para ajudar o seu pai com esta carga formidvel de trabalho.

programme.desc: Our unique story spans a decade and follows one of Tanzania's most powerful lion prides as they overcome mounting obstacles by relying on strong family bonds. Then, Dr. Emily and Dr. Nicole team up for a farm call to see a cow with a retained placenta - or so they think!

programme.title: The Incredible Dr. Pol 7 S7 E1
programme.desc: Summer is in full swing in central Michigan and Pol Vet Services has revved up to meet the growing needs of their clients - from farm calls to clinic emergencies, Dr. Pol and crew are full speed ahead. But animals are not the only ones in need of Dr. Pol's attention, as he and Charles embark on a mission to fix up his vintage DMC DeLorean for the local car show. The car will have to wait though, as the Pol duo have the pedal to the metal en route to a serious emergency - Bow Tie, a beloved family cow has suffered an enormous prolapse after giving birth. The longer the uterus is out the more it swells, so time is of the essence if they are to save Bow Tie in this emergency farm call. While Dr. Pol and Charles have their hands full, Dr. Brenda is headed to Caryl Dairy where the situation is grim for a cow struggling to give birth. With zero progress made since Dr. Brenda's arrival, the focus shifts from delivering the calf to saving the mother. Dr. Brenda resorts to a last ditch effort - a bovine cesarean section - in order to save the mother. As it sits, the DeLorean sounds more like a wheezing goat than a purring kitten - it needs some TLC from Doc and Charles. After discovering electrical issues in the car, it's a race to the finish getting it ready to show at the Mount Pleasant car show. Where's the flux capacitor when you need it?!

programme.title: SpongeBob SquarePants S7 E5
programme.desc: The character-driven cartoon chronicles the nautical and often nonsensical adventures of SpongeBob, an incurably optimistic and earnest sea sponge, and his underwater friends. Dwelling a few fathoms beneath the tropical isle of Bikini Atoll in the sub-surface city of Bikini Bottom, SpongeBob lives in a two-story pineapple. Instead of taking the logical approach to everyday challenges, SpongeBob approaches life in a wayward and unconventional way. Whether searching for the ultimate spatula to perfect his burger flipping technique at the Krusty Krab or just hanging out with his best friend Patrick (an amiable starfish), SpongeBob's good intentions and overzealous approach to life usually create chaos in his underwater world.

programme.title: Dragon Ball Z S1 E248
programme.desc: Dragon Ball Z continues the adventures of Goku, who, along with his companions, defend the Earth against villains ranging from aliens (Frieza), androids (Cell) and other creatures (Majin Buu). While the original Dragon Ball anime followed Goku from childhood to early adulthood, Dragon Ball Z is a continuation of his adult life, but at the same time parallels the life of his son, Gohan, as well as the development of his rival Vegeta.

programme.title: LoliRock S1 E50
programme.desc: LoliRock follows the journey of young Iris, a spirited teenage girl with a beautiful voice and an unending desire to help others. When Iris joins the girl group LoliRock, her life is changed forever, as a new world of music, mysteries and magical powers is revealed. These three new friends are now bound together by their destinies as magical princesses and a fight against injustice. Marathon Media (creators of Totally Spies!) have once again created a cast of characters that are aspirational and serves as role models to a generation of children for whom justice has become a central value. With experienced, world renowned talent, and proven producers, LoliRock is sure to connect with every girl's magical inner self.

programme.title: The Long Ballad E9

Although Baili Hongxuan and Baili Hongshuo, sons of the deceased prince, were loyal to the young emperor, Baili Hongxuan had repeatedly won military exploits to keep the people of Yuguo safe. programme.title: Brothers E442
programme.desc: Ador is a model police officer dedicated to the ideals of service, honor and justice.He is respected by his community and well-loved by his family and peers. But Ador suddenly disappears in a police operation against human trafficking.His wife, young son and his grandmother are worried, but his superior tells them that he is seriously wounded and recovering in a safe house. A week after, Ador returns to his family and duty.Everyone around him feels that he behaves differently.There are events in the past he cannot remember and he does things he is not accustomed to do.Ador's loved ones try to understand that this is caused by trauma from the past encounter. But what they don't know is that Ador is already dead.And the person living with them is his long-lost twin brother, Cardo.Cardo is asked to take his brother's place to find out who is behind the human trafficking syndicate and weed out some police officers protecting it. While Cardo makes it his personal mission to avenge his brother's death, he has to deal with old wounds that separated him from Ador.He also finds himself slowly falling in love with his brother's wife and finding fulfillment in being a father to his brother's son.What awaits Cardo when he has to face the truth in the end?

programme.title: Irreplaceable E29
programme.desc: Emerging from a terrible event that changes the course of his life, Emman finds a stable job and lives a simple life in the province of Alcala with his father and brother. Blessings continue to come Emman's way when he reunites with his son, Robbie, for the child's birthday celebration and finally buries the hatchet with his ex-wife Celine. However, Celine's fianc Anton cannot help but burn with jealousy despite her continued reassurance. As their reunion nears its end, things take a turn for the worse when an unidentified man takes Robbie captive in broad daylight. The story of Emman's and Celine's loss is every parent's nightmare. To lose one's child is devastating, and to lose them to an organ trafficking syndicate preying on defenseless and innocent children is an abomination. The couple, once estranged, come together to search for their son, and discover their love for one another is still there. In the process, they discover the betrayal of people they trust, and the evil permeating within their community.

programme.title: A Soldier's Heart E7
programme.desc: The series primarily focuses on the soldiers of the4th Infantry Divisionof thePhilippine Armyand their actions during combat. Through multiple perspectives, the story focuses on these soldiers, mainly: Alex Marasigan, an IT expert who quits his desk job and joins because just like his brother, he wants to serve the country, Abraham "Abe" Kamlun, a Tausug Muslim man, who, despite his family's opposition of the move, joins the Army nonetheless, and Michael Mendoza, a boy who joins the Army to provide for his family. The series also focuses on their Moro separatist adversaries, led by Saal Alhuraji, also known by his nom de guerre Abdul Waajid, who seeks to avenge his father who was killed by the military.

programme.title: I'll Never Say Goodbye E13
programme.desc: Amid a beautiful island in their youth, Waldo and Aryann were once deeply in love. But they are tor apart by tragedy, when Waldo goes to jail after accidentally killing Aryann's uncle who attempted to molest her. Aryann does everything she can to get Waldo out of prison and later finds herself being forced into prostitution. On her first night as an escort, she meets Tristan, a rich man who unexpectedly does not take advantage of her vulnerability. Nothing happens between them, but Tristan leaves Aryann a large sum of money, enough to hire a lawyer who helps free Waldo. Their happiness is short-lived, when the revenge-seeking brother of Aryann's uncle ends up shooting Waldo. With his body nowhere to be found, Aryann presumes Waldo is dead. It turns out that a nurse named Leila saved and treated Waldo until he recovered from his post-traumatic disorder. But by the time he returns to his hometown. Waldo learns Aryann has moved on and already started a new life in the city. Years pass, and as Waldo pursues his dream of becoming a marine engineer, a twist of fate reunites him with his former flame. His boss Tristan introduces him to his fiancee, who is none other than his one great love, Aryann, now a successful lawyer. When their paths collide, old wounds and feelings resurface as they try to resist one another. Waldo and Aryann's love story has been marred by time and circumstance, and worse, is now imperilled by Tristan and bitter rivals. Will their undying love survive the odds?

programme.title: Irreplaceable E31

programme.title: I'll Never Say Goodbye E15
programme.desc: Amid a beautiful island in their youth, Waldo and Aryann were once deeply in love. Nothing happens between them, but Tristan leaves Aryann a large sum of money, enough to hire a lawyer who helps free Waldo. Their happiness is short-lived, when the revenge-seeking brother of Aryann's uncle ends up shooting Waldo. With his body nowhere to be found, Aryann presumes Waldo is dead. It turns out that a nurse named Leila saved and treated Waldo until he recovered from his post-traumatic disorder. But by the time he returns to his hometown. Waldo learns Aryann has moved on and already started a new life in the city. Years pass, and as Waldo pursues his dream of becoming a marine engineer, a twist of fate reunites him with his former flame. His boss Tristan introduces him to his fiancee, who is none other than his one great love, Aryann, now a successful lawyer. When their paths collide, old wounds and feelings resurface as they try to resist one another. Waldo and Aryann's love story has been marred by time and circumstance, and worse, is now imperilled by Tristan and bitter rivals. Will their undying love survive the odds?

How will Kakay protect and defend her child from the accusations? What is the role of Troy Ramones', the mayor of Sidero, in the life of Rica and Kakay?

programme.title: The General's Daughter E57
programme.desc: 2nd LT Rhian Bonifacio is a Military Nurse for the AFP and is dedicated in saving lives. But she has a secret. Believing that what she's doing is for the good of all, what will she do when she discovers that everything she's fighting for is a lie? That Tiago, the father she has known and loved all her life is the real enemy using her against her real father, Marcial?

programme.title: The General's Daughter E63
programme.desc: 2nd LT Rhian Bonifacio is a Military Nurse for the AFP and is dedicated in saving lives. But she has a secret. programme.title: Brothers E476
programme.desc: Ador is a model police officer dedicated to the ideals of service, honor and justice.He is respected by his community and well-loved by his family and peers. But Ador suddenly disappears in a police operation against human trafficking.His wife, young son and his grandmother are worried, but his superior tells them that he is seriously wounded and recovering in a safe house. A week after, Ador returns to his family and duty.Everyone around him feels that he behaves differently.There are events in the past he cannot remember and he does things he is not accustomed to do.Ador's loved ones try to understand that this is caused by trauma from the past encounter. But what they don't know is that Ador is already dead.And the person living with them is his long-lost twin brother, Cardo.Cardo is asked to take his brother's place to find out who is behind the human trafficking syndicate and weed out some police officers protecting it. While Cardo makes it his personal mission to avenge his brother's death, he has to deal with old wounds that separated him from Ador.He also finds himself slowly falling in love with his brother's wife and finding fulfillment in being a father to his brother's son.What awaits Cardo when he has to face the truth in the end?

programme.title: Viral Scandal E30
programme.desc: Kakay is an OFW who has been working abroad while her husband Dan works as a furniture maker. By working abroad, she hopes to provide a better future for her family. She thinks her sacrifices have been paying off now that her eldest Rica is on the verge of finishing her apprenticeship in an architectural firm and is about to take the board. Their real-life nightmare begins when Rica gets involved in a video that goes viral. As soon as Kakay learns about the scandal, she comes home to face the judgment and censure of the people around them. Aside from her family, she will also get support from her trusted friend and protector, Kyle, played by Joshua. How will Rica be able to prove her innocence in the said video? How will Kakay protect and defend her child from the accusations? What is the role of Troy Ramones', the mayor of Sidero, in the life of Rica and Kakay?

programme.title: LA VEUVE BLANCHE E168
programme.desc: Dulaari verse un seau d'eau sur Dhaani pour nettoyer la couleur. Dhaani pleure sans arrt. Viplav et ses amis tranent dehors et s'assoient prs du feu de joie. Il dit qu'il doit faire la dernire chose avant d'aller en Amrique et sourit. Ses amis essaient de l'arrter pendant qu'il s'en va. Il ajoute secrtement du vin dans le pot de Dhaani et se cache. Il pense que ce sera amusant maintenant...

programme.title: LA RIVIRE DU DESTIN E19
programme.desc: En 1845, la maison d'Antnia est mise sac par une tribu d'amrindiens. La jeune femme est sauve par Apoena, l'un d'entre eux, dont elle tombe rapidement amoureuse. Cette idylle n'est pas du got de Laru, la femme d'Apoena, qui, l'aide d'un puissant shaman, jette un sort sur Antnia ainsi que sur toute sa descendance si ces derniers s'aventurent prs des rives de l'Araguaya. Des annes plus tard, la famille de Solano, l'arrire-petit-fils d'Antnia commence tre victime de la maldiction.

programme.title: FLEUR SAUVAGE S1 E14
programme.desc: L'histoire suit Lily Cruz, une belle hritire qui veut que justice soit rendue pour la mort de son pre Dante et pour l'assaut de la mre Camia et la folie qui en rsulte, en cherchant se venger de la famille perverse des Ardiente, puissante dynastie politique de la province fictive qui porte leur nom. La famille Ardiente est la plus puissante dynastie politique de la province sous la juridiction du gouverneur Julio Ardiente et de sa fille Emilia, maire de la municipalit (Poblacion Ardiente). Raul, avec le droit des puissants, agresse Camia et incite Dante porter plainte pour viol. Le monde de Lily s'effondre lorsque Dante meurt de manire suspecte d'une crise cardiaque et qu'elle est tmoin du viol de sa mre. Bien que cibls pour tre tus, les assassins ressentent de la compassion pour la fillette de 9 ans et la librent la place.

programme.title: L'HRITRIRE E70
programme.desc: Romina Andrada (Beauty Gonzalez), une secrtaire devenue pouse du magnat des affaires Robert Mondragon (Albert Martinez), qui l'a pouse bien qu'elle ait t viole et portait l'enfant de l'agresseur. l'insu de Romina, c'est Daniela (Dimples Romana), la fille de Robert, qui avait orchestr son enlvement juste avant de sduire le fianc de Romina, Carlos Bartolom (Adrian Alandy)

programme.title: The Promise of Chang'an E16
programme.desc: Helan Mingyu, the granddaughter of the lord of Yonglin, has been smart since childhood, and the boy met Xiao Chengxu, the ninth prince of Shengzhou, by accident. The news of Xiao Chengxu's "death in battle" was misrepresented. In order to save Chengxu's younger brother Xiao Chengxuan, Mingyu was forced to marry Chengxu's third brother, Xiao Chengrui, the king of Shengzhou, and was trapped in the harem. Xiao Chengxu repeatedly made military exploits to help Xiao Chengrui become emperor and establish the Dasheng Kingdom. Before he succeeded, Xiao Chengrui relapsed and died suddenly, and ordered Mingyu's son Xiao Qiyuan to succeed him in order to contain Xiao Chengxu and stabilize the court. Xiao Chengxu was forced to support Xiao Qiyuan, but he still wanted to marry Helan Mingyu. At the same time, Qi Yuan gradually grew up, dissatisfied with Xiao Chengxu's control, and even learned of his mother's affair with Xiao Chengxu under the provocation of others, and resented both of them. Helan Mingyu focused on the stability of Dasheng, and tried his best to find a balance between Qiyuan and Xiao Chengxu. Unexpectedly, Chengxu died in the battle, and Qiyuan was born with a love affair, and passed away with his favorite concubine Dong Ruoxuan. For the future of Dasheng, Mingyu once again accompanies the little emperor who is enthroned.

programme.title: Shaolin Wooden Men
programme.desc: A young boy witnesses the death of his father at the hands of a mysterious masked kung fu expert. As he grows older, he becomes a mute, and trains at Shaolin to become strong so he can one day avenge his father. Little does he know, one of his known teachers, a prisoner in the temple's strongholds, is actually his father's killer. (Little Mute is an orphan traumatized into silence by the death of his father at the hands of a vicious fighting master. Living at the Shaolin monastery, he befriends a dangerous prisoner who teaches him a secret form of deadly kung fu. Seeing his intense determination, other masters share the wisdom of the Gliding Snake and Drunken Master techniques. In one of the most exciting fight scenes ever filmed, Little Mute must run the gauntlet of the famous 108 wooden men in an extreme test of skill and endurance. But if he becomes a master, will he use his unmatched force for redemption or revenge?)

Otvio piloto e chega na fazenda precisando de dinheiro, pois perdeu o emprego e quer que as terras sejam vendidas. programme.title: Mar de Amor
programme.desc: Nossa histria comea no porto de Miami quando, na proa de um belo iate, Coral, uma mulher to bonita quanto m, grita com raiva para um homem que ele no pode deix-la. Coral uma assassina Passam-se vrios meses Estrella Marina uma menina jovem e linda, mas rebelde, franca e honesta. Ela acorda todas as manhs esperando que seus sonhos se tornem realidade naquele dia.
